title: 2020 Week 16 Recap
itunes:title: 2020 Week 16 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler recap every game from week 16 starting with the Steeler's get right game against the Colts (2:29). The heroes hit the Seahawks win over the Rams (9:48), peak Fitzmagic (16:47), and Alvin Kamara's huge game (24:33). Nick Shook joins to talk the Cowboys win (42:05), and him and Marc suffer through the Jets/ Browns recap. Aaron Rodgers is on fire - we end the show with a SNF recap (1:22:45.
